Advantages of an On premise server over cloud server

1. We can create a n number of website end points.
	Example: 1. research.domain.com
	         2. Exam.domain.com
		 3. library.domain.com
2. Security: It almost equally secure to cloud because
	1. It is a Linux server
	2. All the security standards have been taken care
	
3. Data Control:The data is under our control
4. Operation Cost: The operation cost is negligible compare to cloud.
5. Customization: It is easier to customize the on-premise server
6. Speed :  Compare to Cloud, On-premise servers are faster as the server is dedicated to only our application, where as low operation cost cloud servers are mostly shared servers.
	